{"tid":1388051,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"唔該大家出去做咩都好，記得帶裝備出去","createTime":"2019-07-30T15:45:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-30T16:03:23.000Z","uid":215011,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"5d6076237407e0b48b685ea28d4d9280c9393693","tid":1388051,"uid":215011,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T15:45:07.000Z","msg":"我唔理你地去行街食飯，返工返學呀<br />\n都同我帶啲基本返工裝備！！！<br />\n<br />\n一來你唔知會唔會突然有工返，要出去<br />\n<br />\n二來，你唔知工地幾時有意外，唔係次次都無意外<br />\n可以唔受傷咁離場，就算本身個工地做足安全措施<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，都同我照帶，你都知工地有幾變幻無常，成日有意外架啦，粉塵吸到入口入眼就唔好啦，比啲硬物打到到個頭都唔好啦<br />\n<br />\n大家加油，努力返工<br />\n建設美好香港<br />\n<br />\n利申:職安真漢子"},{"pid":"c5e25289aee02cf0fcc5e84de4b503f357e75f6b","tid":1388051,"uid":215011,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T15:46:19.000Z","msg":"等我自推下先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ebb1548022b7c56fa60d5d8c4a81cb1c9692300","tid":1388051,"uid":215011,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T15:48:40.000Z","msg":"推呀"},{"pid":"2b267b314fda593c29720bba809c2da60240f85b","tid":1388051,"uid":215011,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T15:48:52.000Z","msg":"我再推"},{"pid":"805cb9d1fd815742d85fa9d4463a41e697532440","tid":1388051,"uid":238275,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T15:49:01.000Z","msg":"聽朝九點，西灣河東區法院，聲援義士。"},{"pid":"615357e7552bef8b703b40512593d93c1e84e350","tid":1388051,"uid":215011,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"805cb9d1fd815742d85fa9d4463a41e697532440","tid":1388051,"uid":238275,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T15:49:01.000Z","msg":"聽朝九點，西灣河東區法院，聲援義士。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T15:49:52.000Z","msg":"啱呀，聽日仲有架"},{"pid":"e24ca090fa8b35bd251207500a14341e2b383bc5","tid":1388051,"uid":182088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T15:49:59.000Z","msg":"頭盔